game.name: Vampire Nose Doctor
game.description:
Hey woman! No need to be scared of this vampire woman who is already struggling with a big nose problem. She needs a doctor who could help make her nose healthy again. You are the best doctor in the city so the vampire has just approached you for her nose surgery. Do not waste your time anymore. Grab your medical tools and be prepared to show your intense doctoring abilities to provide her with the best treatment for her nose in Vampire Nose Doctor!

You have got a wonderful opportunity to gain worldwide popularity in this brand new girls game. Start by making her nostrils bigger by fixing the re-tractor! This will give you better visibility in her nose. Then hydrate her nose by spraying some water on the affected area. Now grab a pair of sharp scissors to clear the nose from the big hair chunks. Pull out the single ones with a pair of tweezers and then clean each of her nostrils using a soft cotton stick. Give three pimples that are on the top of her nose proper care in this HTML5 doctor game!

In the next step, use a magnifying glass to have a closer look inside her nose. This will make sure that if there are no harmful bacteria and viruses in her nose. Keep your eyes on the info bubble you see on the left side of the screen to check which equipment you can go with to remove each virus from her nose! This is a stressful situation for the lady so try to keep resting her time to time in this medical simulation game. Try out more top liked free doctoring games for girls to have a blast!
